wiki.summary: Appearing as the outro to Disc 1 on Don Toliver’s 2024 album HARDSTONE PSYCHO, ATTITUDE features Cash Cobain and Charlie Wilson. Toliver premiered this song at his Abu Dhabi show on 4/27/24. The song leaked in full on 5/8/2024. Toliver announced on 5/21/2024 that the song would premier on Wednesday 5/22/2024 at 12 pm ET. The release date for HARDSTONE PSYCHO was announced alongside the release for ATTITUDE. Read more on Last.fm.
